test_158,3,6,"Yes, I like the consistency much better. I also think that pudding has more of a flavor than jello. Which do you like better? Jello or pudding?"
test_158,3,7,I also prefer pudding.  The texture feels so creamy and succulent in my mouth.  It's so good for how cheap it is.
