test_166,3,0,"I saw an interesting documentary about shark diving, they are not attracted to the blood in the water. Did you know about that ?"
test_166,3,1,"No, I had no idea. That'll make me feel much safer when I go diving. What are they attracted to then?"
test_166,3,2,I've heard sharks have a good sense of smell.  I was surprised to hear that it wasn't the blood since that's what you typically see in the movies etc.
test_166,3,3,I had no idea. That's so interesting! That makes movies like Jaws completely different in real life. Does that make you any less worried about sharks when you go scuba diving sometime? 
